Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:25.77,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}为了荣耀!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:31.13,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}来吧 多舛命运已然成形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:35.29,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}屏息以盼那必然到来的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.13,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.35,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}Hey! 若你想赢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.78,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}那你最好机伶点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:49.00,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}没有其他选择
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.13,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}唯有智慧主宰一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.88,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}逼近灭顶的负面思考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:02.27,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}漫天乌云的阴郁情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:12.10,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}饱受煎熬的日子 如今迎来终结
