Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:21.14,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}没错 此刻正是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.20,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}努力的结晶将大放异彩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.05,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}纵情咆啸!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:26.79,OPTC,,0,0,0,,{\r\fad(200, 200)\be2}为那荣耀!
